text: William Byers (1831–1903) was a Nebraska politician. William Byers may also refer to: *William P. Byers (born 1943), Canadian mathematician and philosopher *William Byers, namesake of Byers, Colorado *Billy Byers (1927–1996), American jazz trombonist and arranger ==See also== *Will Byers, fictional character *Bill Byers (1877–1948), baseball player
title: William Byers (disambiguation)
